snippet.title: Momodora I 100% Walkthrough PART 1 (PC) No Commentary Action Platformer
snippet.description:
Momodora I Game Playthrough PART 1 (PC) No Commentary.
Momodora I is the first game in the Momodora series. The game follows the story of Isadora, an orphaned child who goes into a forbidden land to attempt to resurrect her mother. It's meant to be challenging like an "arcade" game.

Full Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL1TtvzJyZhgJwOAaYwqnsSeII50Qrn_pu
